Joan Gardner (voice actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joan_Gardner_(voice_actor) 0 Joan Gardner (November 16, 1926 – December 10, 1992) was an American actress who was most active in voice over roles. She was also a screenwriter, songwriter, author and composer. Joan_Gardner ( November_16_,_1926 – December_10_,_1992 ) was an_American_actress who was most_active in voice over roles .
